description:
The "DiaCard - ECG Recorder" software is designed to work with ECG recorders of 06000.1, 06000.2, 06000.33, 06000.34, 06000.35, 06000.4, 06000.6, 06000.7 and 12010 models. The application is a component of internet-monitoring system ‚ÄúTelecardian‚Äù, that is a part of Holter system ‚ÄúDiaCard‚Äù.

     Features:
‚Ä¢ modes: "Electrocardiograph", "Stress test", "Event monitor", "Holter";
‚Ä¢ ECG viewing in 1, 3, 6 (7) or 12 channels, tuning speed and scale;
‚Ä¢ saving ECG records (duration from 10 seconds to 168 hours) to the Archive (internal memory of the tablet, smartphone);
‚Ä¢ digital filtering: 0.01Hz, 0.05Hz, 0.1Hz, 25Hz, 35Hz, 50/60Hz, 75Hz, ADS, Finger Electrodes Filter;
‚Ä¢ real-time calculation and display of heart rate, electrode breakage control;
‚Ä¢ setting alarms: bradycardia, tachycardia, pause, arrhythmia, no signal;
‚Ä¢ adding text comments to any recorded fragment;
‚Ä¢ operation in the "client‚Äìserver" mode: remote viewing of ECG and managing the recorder;
‚Ä¢ for the "Stress test" mode - full control over the operation of Kettler ergometers of the E and X series;
‚Ä¢ for the "Event Monitor" mode - preparation for stand-alone operation (without an Android device), start the research, stop, read records made by the button (on demand), on schedule, on alarm (by signs: tachycardia, bradycardia, arrhythmia, pause, no signal);
‚Ä¢ for the "Holter" mode - preparation for stand-alone operation (without an Android device), start the research, stop;
‚Ä¢ automatic and manual sending of records to e-mail, to the Telecardian system, to cloud storages or to a hospital information system (on request);
‚Ä¢ generating reports, output to a stationary (Wi-Fi) printer, or in a file (pdf);
‚Ä¢ fast printing of any ECG section on a portable Bluetooth thermal printer;
‚Ä¢ ECG data export to HL7 aEcg, Fazagraf formats;
‚Ä¢ viewing records made in the SCP-ECG format (without saving to the Archive);
‚Ä¢ integration with other systems and services
(SDK & API - on request);
‚Ä¢ monitoring and updating of recorder‚Äôs firmware;
